Sirqul SDK for Native Android OS

Packages 
Package Description
com.sirqul.sdk
Contains main Sirqul.java class.
com.sirqul.sdk.api
Contains management classes and interface, a few of which subclasses are created to support organizing various API services.
com.sirqul.sdk.api.application
Contains API classes that fall under the Application category.
com.sirqul.sdk.api.billing
Contains API classes that fall under the Billing category.
com.sirqul.sdk.api.common
Contains API classes that fall under the Common category.
com.sirqul.sdk.api.games
Contains API classes that fall under the Games category.
com.sirqul.sdk.api.location
Contains API classes that fall under the Location category.
com.sirqul.sdk.api.objectStore
Contains API classes that fall under the ObjectStore category.
com.sirqul.sdk.api.offers
Contains API classes that fall under the Offers category.
com.sirqul.sdk.api.route
Contains API classes that fall under the Route category.
com.sirqul.sdk.comparators
Contains comparators used within parts of the SDK.
com.sirqul.sdk.custom
Contains custom instances of various classes used within the SDK.
com.sirqul.sdk.data
Contains data classes and types referenced throughout the SDK and various response classes.
com.sirqul.sdk.exceptions
Contains custom Exception class types.
com.sirqul.sdk.helpers
Contains helper classes designed to add convenience and usability.
com.sirqul.sdk.interfaces
Contains various interfaces used throughout the SDK.
com.sirqul.sdk.responses
Contains response classes of which json responses are mapped to using Gson.
com.sirqul.sdk.responsesJackson
Contains legacy response classes of which json responses are mapped to using Gson.
com.sirqul.sdk.services
Contains services that are supplied for convenience and specific functionality.
com.sirqul.sdk.widget
Contains custom widget classes that can ease development.

Contains a SirqulArrayAdapter class which allows you to only have to choose a data type, to supply a layout resource of your choice, and a SirqulViewWrapper instance based off your chosen data type and layout resource.
